{
  "stem": "214.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the first time I ate a non-Kosher meal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was in it a-- it was-- it was sort of like a nightclub.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't-- what would you call it here?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a-- there was dancing, there was music.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A dinner club.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A dinner club, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], it was called.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there I come, you know, and he treats me like his best girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we talk about literature a little bit, we talk about this a little bit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he asked me to dance, and I dance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he ordered some drinks and I drink.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I just-- you know, when I think of it, me at that time, I was-- I was-- what was I?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not quite 19 or 20 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But suddenly I am a Pole among the Poles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was very gentlemanly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he showed me all those papers and he signed this-- of course, I had all the instructions from my cousin.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, what-- and then he takes me back to-- in the evening, takes me-- I mean, to the-- I took the train back and came to Skierniewice, and that's how that thing started.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So-- and that's when, since we had, you know, those buses-- buses-- actually, trucks, these were trucks-- going either to Krakow, either to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Whoever wanted to go to Warsaw or to Miedzyrzec, whoever wanted to go to Miedzyrzec.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And many people still, you know, they had family in Warsaw, and nobody knew how to know how bad it's going-- it's going to be.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "People were going also to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And Bernard's family-- his mother, his brother, and he-- went to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that gave me again-- I think of it-- a chance to travel to Warsaw several times.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
